{"type": "article", "id": 34515, "title": "历峰集团或将再度裁员，以及，耐克的玫瑰金合作款比较浮夸 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2016-11-16T02:34:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 4556, "name": "G-Shock"}, {"id": 15797, "name": "工装"}, {"id": 34907, "name": "MADNESS"}, {"id": 34908, "name": "Baby-G"}, {"id": 68, "name": "苹果"}, {"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}, {"id": 2816, "name": "Kate Spade"}, {"id": 3289, "name": "梅西百货"}, {"id": 4579, "name": "历峰集团"}, {"id": 9021, "name": "余文乐"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 25, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161116101836WpB0gKvNdIS18X7n.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/retail/macys-thanksgiving-day-parade-costs-an-estimated-10-4-million-to-12-3-million-10706078/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>梅西百货今年的感恩节游行计划斥资高达 1230 万美元</b></a> | 梅西百货一年一度的感恩节游行能吸引 5000 万电视观众及 350 万的现场观众。今年是梅西百货的第 90 个感恩节活动，它计划花 1040 至 1230 万美元，打造一个 8000 人的感恩节游行队伍。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.businessinsider.com/kate-spade-activist-hedge-fund-caerus-investors-letter-2016-11\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>对冲基金敦促 Kate Spade 出售</b></a> | 自 2014 年 8 月以来，Kate Spade 的股价两年下跌了 63%。Kate Spade 的股东之一，纽约对冲基金 Caerus Investors 表示，希望 Kate Spade 能够公开寻求出售。消息传出之后，Kate Spade 的股价在周一大涨了 7.8%。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.thefashionlaw.com/home/alaia-chloe-cartier-parent-co-to-cut-up-to-250-jobs\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>业绩低迷，历峰集团或将大幅裁员</b></a> | 世界第二大奢侈品集团历峰上半财年的销售同比下跌了 12.6%。有消息称，历峰集团计划进一步从集团的瑞士手表制作部门削减 200 到 250 个职位。如果消息属实，加上今年五月削减的 300 个职位，历峰集团裁员将累计超过 500 个。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p class=\"\">为纪念 1996 年圣诞特别版 「Lover’s Collection」LOV96-2  套装推出 20 周年，<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/11/g-shock-baby-glovers-collection20\" rel=\"nofollow\">G-Shock 与 Baby-G 重新推出全白色的复刻版</a>，除了表带上绣有 「Lover’s Collection 20th Anniversary」字样之外，其他部分皆还原了 20 年前的款式，这个复刻版手表计划在 11 月内推出。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611161010416HGhmKR2E837XLoT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116101054IL9YF8PjUoAvByHh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116101054D0nU9NERbQfYG5L7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.racked.com/2016/11/15/13631374/nike-rose-gold-sneakers-bandier\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nike 和健身零售商 Bandier 合作推出玫瑰金 mini collection</a>。该系列包括运动背心、leggings、以及六款不同的鞋，以玫瑰金的元素贯穿其中。鞋子售价 115 美元，该系列目前只在纽约的 Flatiron Bandier store 出售，可以寄送到世界各地。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116101112vUbXRaZBlG8xKjTq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666304\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116101128h1zb8GVEjuxrtDZp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611161011353nk7TXr5mEZhClKY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>在品牌成立 30 周年之际，Apple 首推设计书籍。在该书中记录了过年 20 年的 Apple 设计，以 500 张照片及插画的形式结构了设计团队 20 年来的创新设计。这本<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/11/apple-designed-by-apple-in-california-20\" rel=\"nofollow\">《Designed by Apple in California》</a>将有两个不同的尺寸版本，定价分别为 199 和 299 美元，今天正式登陆香港、台湾等个别城市的 Apple 官网。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116101207eLHUVvbWmA3u8n61.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116101300PgZ6aMhG2JX7rtFY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611161013078hsJ2iFcLP3AfxyE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611161013161kjVpa3tEoTJ8O05.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116101316xGjYM4T5CfnX7VEt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">余文乐的潮牌<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/11/madness-x-carhartt-wip-2016\" rel=\"nofollow\"> MADNESS 和美国工装品牌 Carhartt WIP 再度合作</a>，带来了以爱因斯坦的相对论和 Peace 主题的系列单品。这个系列将于本月 19 日正式上架。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116101359tY6bfe91Sg8dvQUm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667806\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611161013598of7hw6Vi9eZDQ14.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667806\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116101359DA7Oqt1i5MwThBre.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667806\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116101359o5sEjFpAqRkxz3JI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667806\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116101359ljE6GaeTCfy08P4I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667806\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116101359tyHzNk9bcGRxrCET.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667806\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116101400hJlGLCDKuHVwt7vn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667806\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116101400jpTkdl8MqYWQ5Nuy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667806\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116101359y5z7B0latgv6G3EQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667806\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116101400JDyNs2OWxBpTaSIr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667806\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611161014009HgA0vcT5iutBRLf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667806\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116101400YhtDSe4fw6xRHiV9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667806\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116101410heUHmrgKZkx5YATu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667806\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016111610141173gf2nzjFcCwrOT6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667806\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">圣诞季临近，<a href=\"http://popbee.com/accessories/gucci-holiday-2016-collection/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Gucci 也推出了假日系列</a>。在经典的 Gucci logo 上加入不同的动物刺绣图案，包括钱包、钥匙扣、手机壳和卡套等一系列单品。<span style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</span></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116101420K4jm5kLOxQFuUCdJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116101433rA47SuIDZv0T82O9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116101433n6D9jlVrYba8N3RE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611161014347ZdoklH3UYnXrNJP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116101434HCgVFuJ23SBhr16A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116101434k1luXOvWdH943qJT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161116101435txIUkqzhC0a4jQo6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">&nbsp;</p>"}